		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Help on quading<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Help on quading";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Mar 4th 9:39 PM2004 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=107845432730450&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=8&mid=107845432730450&num=6&post=1&replyto=107845432730450"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=107845432730450></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=308925"><span id=>hizzouse</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />2 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=hizzouse&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I am really new at everquest and decided to start with a Druid.&nbsp;&nbsp;I see everyone talking about quading, can someone please tell me what this is and how to go about doing this?  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >6 Replies</td></tr></table>
